accountants and other financial professionals… on a temporary basis founder robert half had previously managed the hiring of accounting staff for a sizeable textile manufacturing concern and saw an opportunity as no placement agency had been focusing on this sector of the marketselfpublished source in the mid to lates robert half rh altered its prior focus—which had been like that of the field in general—from relatively undifferentiated temporary clerical and light industry staffing to providing temporary workers at higher skill levels via new professional staffing divisionsselfpublished source having grown to over  locations in the united states and launched an aggressive campaign to repurchase many of the separate franchises the firm went public in  then expanded its operations into europe in  in addition to their accountemps brand the firm expanded to include specialty groups focusing on technology legal and creative services personnel inroads into the legal sector began with the companys  acquisition of the affiliates a firm in southern california that placed temporary and permanent paralegal legal administrative and other legal support personnel with it being renamed as robert half legal robert half went on to establish itself as a key information provider for government agencies and others seeking statistics and trends regarding employmentwhen with its marketspecific salary guides being used as a resource by the us department of labor in the preparation of their own forecasts in addition to their main staffing line of business rh also provides independent risk consulting internal audit and information technology consulting services via its protiviti subsidiary which was founded in  with the acquisition of former employees of arthur andersen since then the group has grown from  to over  staffselfpublished source and continues to be led by andersen alumnicitation needed in  the company was finally able to buy back the last of the few remaining independent franchise operations published worksedit founder robert halfs tradition of authoring books on the industry—such as making it big in data processingfull citation needed and how to get a better job in this crazy worldfull citation needed—was continued by the ceo of this datewhen harold m max messmercitation needed in the form of works like job hunting for dummiesfull citation needed see alsoedit human resource consulting arthur andersen protiviti referencesedit  a b c d rh intl staff  history and values roberthalfbe archived from the original company web page on june   retrieved february   selfpublished sourcethirdparty source needed  rh intl staff  about us roberthalfcom archived from the original company web page on march   retrieved february   selfpublished sourcethirdparty source needed  rh intl staff march   robert half international named to worlds most admired archived from the original press release on october   retrieved february   thirdparty source neededselfpublished source  sia and workforcecom staffs  the hot list i worlds largest staffing companies pdf staffing industry analysts staffingindustrycom archived from the original pdf on february   – via workforcecom quote note results reflect revenue for  or most recent fiscal year for which information is available  source staffing industry analysts wwwstaffingindustrycom staffing industry analysts a unit of workforce management parent crain communications compiled the list and established the ranking based on public filings information provided from companies and an annual survey   a b c d e f g h i j fu staff wernick e et al  robert half international inc history fundinguniversecom retrieved february   cs maint multiple names authors list link this information is derived from the following source wernick ellen  gariepy jennifer  robert half international inc in grant tina international directory of company histories idch idch gale reference library derdak thomas series ed vol  detroit mi galest james press isbn 