ood but will also generate signals later than when using shorter term averages rhi stock price revealed optimistic move of  comparing average price of last  days this comparison showed up direction of price above its sma the beta factor is volatility shows sense of how far the stock will fall if the market takes a dive and how high stock will rise if the bull starts to climb a stock with a beta more than  means high volatile and less than  means low volatile the pe ratio of  helps investors explore how much they should pay for a stock based on its current earnings high ratio reveals positive future performance and investors are willing to pay more low ratio discloses poor current and future performance common shareholders want to know how profitable their capital is in the businesses they invest it in the company gives a roe of  the higher the roe the better the company is at generating profits return on assets roa ratio indicates how profitable a company is relative to its total assets the roa is  a company that manages their assets well will have a high return while if manages their assets poorly will have a low return roi is  a positive result means that returns exceed costs analysts therefore consider the investment a net gain the opposite kind of result a negative means that costs outweigh returns analysts therefore view the investment as a net loss related articlesmore from author philip morris international inc pm adjusted down to sma  pattersonuti energy inc pten located below to sma  regal entertainment group rgc adjusted down to sma  leave a reply cancel reply please enter your comment please enter your name here you have entered an incorrect email address please enter your email address here hot stocks wisdomtree investments inc wetf located below to sma  andrew carr  july    steel dynamics inc stld adjusted down to sma  andrew carr  july    suntrust banks inc sti located below to sma  andrew carr  july    technology fang holdings limited sfun stock moves